{
  "texts": [
    "Machine learning helps coordinate these bots to act in swarms or networks.",
    "Coordination of disinformation at scale -real-time social media analysis and strategy adaptation, cross-platform botnet deployment, natural language generation in multiple languages and styles.",
    "AI in counter-disinformation -on the defensive side, AI is used to detect fake content and accounts, as well as to automate factchecking and content moderation.",
    "We now delve into each of the offensive categories (first four) with case studies, and then discuss the defensive use of AI.",
    "AI-generated synthetic media, or deepfakes, have become one of the most visible tools of disinformation."
  ]
}